# Upload Directory

This directory is for uploaded files. The actual uploaded files are ignored by git for security and storage reasons.

## Directory Structure
```
uploads/
├── projects/     # Project-related files
├── tasks/        # Task attachments
├── avatars/      # User profile pictures
├── company/      # Company logos and documents
└── temp/         # Temporary uploads
```

## Security Notes
- All uploaded files are scanned for security threats
- File types are restricted based on whitelist
- Maximum file size limits are enforced
- Files are served with proper headers to prevent execution
